    {
        "SurahNumber": 47,
        "AyahNumber": 11,
        "Tafseer": "\"That is because Allah is the protector of those who have believed and because the disbelievers have no protector.\" (11)\n\nThe Disbelievers Have No Protector\n\nThat is: the true Protector and Sovereign of this universe is Allah Almighty, and He is with the believers; so what weight do the disbelievers carry against Him, when they have no protector. Those whom they assume as their protectors are of no use to them, neither in this world nor in the Hereafter... in verse 3, this same theme has passed in another style. Keep it in view."
